SECTION 2. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 68-11-1607(a), is amended by
deleting "A person shall not perform" and substituting "Except as provided in § 68-11-1303(j), a
person shall not perform".
SECTION 3. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
